WEBVTT

00:00:24.479 --> 00:00:27.083 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Caleb, why aren’t you playing outside?

00:00:27.083 --> 00:00:29.875 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Dad said I’m punished.

00:00:29.875 --> 00:00:32.437 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Oh, I see.

00:00:33.833 --> 00:00:35.624 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
You know Dad loves you,

00:00:35.624 --> 00:00:37.395 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
even when he disciplines you.

00:00:39.125 --> 00:00:40.687 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Oh.

00:00:43.583 --> 00:00:45.333 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Hey,

00:00:45.312 --> 00:00:48.166 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
do you remember
when we planted the fruit tree?

00:00:48.166 --> 00:00:50.187 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Uh-huh.

00:00:59.099 --> 00:01:01.125 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
It grew fast.

00:01:01.125 --> 00:01:04.208 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
But then—

00:01:04.208 --> 00:01:06.291 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
It fell over.

00:01:06.291 --> 00:01:08.416 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
What did Dad do?

00:01:08.416 --> 00:01:10.604 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
He helped it.

00:01:10.583 --> 00:01:12.395 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Right!

00:01:16.266 --> 00:01:19.250 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Did the straps hurt the tree?

00:01:19.250 --> 00:01:21.729 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
No.
They helped it grow straight.

00:01:21.708 --> 00:01:22.812 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Yes!

00:01:22.812 --> 00:01:25.854 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Jehovah and Dad correct you sometimes too,

00:01:25.854 --> 00:01:27.854 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
like the tree.

00:01:27.854 --> 00:01:29.979 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Do you remember what the Bible says?

00:01:29.958 --> 00:01:32.541 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
‘Jehovah disciplines . . . ’

00:01:32.541 --> 00:01:37.187 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Uh, ‘Jehovah disciplines the ones he loves.’

00:01:49.266 --> 00:01:50.895 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Whoa!

00:01:50.874 --> 00:01:52.437 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Oh, Caleb.

00:01:53.416 --> 00:01:55.020 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I love you, Dad.

00:01:56.625 --> 00:01:58.791 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
If discipline is love,

00:01:58.791 --> 00:02:00.812 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
you must love me a whole lot!

00:02:00.812 --> 00:02:03.083 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Yes, Caleb.

00:02:03.083 --> 00:02:04.729 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Yes, I do.

